window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>I don’t know who I am. I only know what I need to be.</i></p> <p>I awoke in a tomb. I had nothing but a big sword and uncertain memories from uncertain lives.</p> <p>I was a great warrior who wandered this land before being killed by an ageless tyrant wizard-king. I was a warrior of a very different sort, who lived in a city of steel and glass.</p> <p>In this life, I’m more than I was–stronger, more powerful, more dangerous. But that wizard-king still lives, and he’s still hunting me.</p> <p>All I have is my sword and my skills. So I’ll gather the gold, weapons, and women I need, and if that wizard gets in my way again...our next meeting will be very different from the last.</p> <p><i>Mercenary of Empyrea </i>is an <i>isekai </i>fantasy adventure in the theme of classic barbarian pulp fiction and contains graphic violence and unconventional relationships.</p>"; 
